    %% External to Ingress
    Client -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>Bearer Token"| Gateway

    %% Ingress to MLflow
    Gateway -->|"HTTPS/8443<br/>TLS (service-ca)<br/>Token passthrough"| MLflow

    %% Operator flows
    Operator -->|"HTTPS/6443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>SA token<br/>Watch + Server-Side Apply"| K8sAPI
    Operator -.->|"creates/manages"| MLflow

    %% MLflow flows
    MLflow -->|"HTTPS/6443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>Delegated user token<br/>SelfSubjectAccessReview"| K8sAPI
    MLflow -->|"HTTPS/443 or HTTP/9000,8333<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>AWS credentials"| S3
    MLflow -->|"PostgreSQL/5432<br/>TLS verify-full<br/>Connection string"| PostgreSQL
    MLflow -->|"MySQL/3306<br/>TLS<br/>Connection string"| MySQL

    %% Metrics
    Prometheus -->|"HTTPS/8443<br/>TLS (service-ca)<br/>Bearer Token"| MLflow
    Prometheus -->|"HTTPS/8443<br/>TLS (service-ca)<br/>Bearer Token + TokenReview"| Operator

